Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.33,0:00:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真要穿這種東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.42,0:00:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別挑肥撿瘦的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.55,0:00:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喏 快瞧 雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.06,0:00:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個很可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.58,0:00:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好土{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.09,0:00:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我自己穿咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.60,0:00:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼還保留著這種生理現象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.15,0:00:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明明{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.43,0:00:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早就死了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,------------
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OP
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天就這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.95,0:02:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.63,0:02:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.75,0:02:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找了午飯給你吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.90,0:02:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這叫午飯?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的神器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.55,0:02:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人的話就是聖旨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神器啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.70,0:02:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.47,0:02:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神器要尊敬主人 為主人奉獻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為主人的手腳工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要學會主動斟茶遞水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想斟茶也沒東西給你斟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准頂嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要順從
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.97,0:02:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會禿啦
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.05,0:03:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}快住手 你這爛貓\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還以為當神明的都會做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果是漫無目的地在城裡亂轉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是避人耳目 在附近祠堂的角落裡縮成一團睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.36,0:03:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日用品也是從垃圾堆撿來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs34\bord0\pos(958,308)\c&H3C3680&}外派電話 夜斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說 那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普及活動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但完全沒人來委託啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是神明?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那眼神是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.77,0:03:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你見識見識我的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正中雅宋_GBK\fs40\c&H000000&\bord0\fsp8\3a&HA0\pos(467,260)}被招來的災厄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和說要上供食物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.73,0:03:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這感召力如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這完全就是敲詐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃完之後 務必要實現我的願望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決定好點什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.93,0:04:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大姐 水要三杯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒?啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非{\rsymbol}…{\r}非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.73,0:04:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜斗你們不是人類 其他人應該看不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是不會被看到 而是不容易引起注意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.40,0:04:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實他們都能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.99,0:04:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.57,0:04:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反過來問你一句
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.39,0:04:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有多少女服務生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不准看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.73,0:04:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唔{\rsymbol}…{\r}兩個?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.03,0:04:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 有四個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和雪音就像被你看漏的兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被當做了背景
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:05:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然一旦被認知 就會作為人類共存於意識中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但很快又會被忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在是太抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就好像你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這城市裡擦身而過的人 你也沒全部記住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.97,0:05:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們由於是彼岸的住民
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.41,0:05:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.06,0:05:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您二位胃口還真是不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,供奉之物不能剩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.55,0:05:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是鐵則
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子會吃壞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神明不蹲大的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 那個人實在是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.11,0:05:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那啥{\rsymbol}…{\r}多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是一歧日和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我日和就行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.85,0:06:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和跟那個是什麼關係
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.76,0:06:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}這些糖給我包一下\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唔{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不小心變成了會靈魂出竅的體質
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.81,0:06:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}這個{\rsymbol}…{\r}\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以想讓夜斗幫忙治好
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.35,0:06:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}為什麼不行\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.83,0:06:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}這不是免費的嗎\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個{\rsymbol}…{\r}雪音君為什麼{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成為夜斗的神器之前 是怎麼樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.01,0:06:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之知道自己死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回過神來時 就在那傢伙手中了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活著時的事情 完全想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.87,0:06:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今後也不知該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.99,0:06:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你{\rsymbol}…{\r}是剛才那隻魚乾小偷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪音君 你喜歡貓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貓好可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.30,0:07:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪音 你剛才想了限制級的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.59,0:07:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了雪音 我告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神明和神器是一心同體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你心中邪念的波動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我作為主人{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.81,0:07:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是會感受到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.25,0:07:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈?這傢伙說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.29,0:07:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個{\rsymbol}…{\r}一心同體是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.42,0:07:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青春期的小鬼真讓人頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.55,0:07:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了 呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呆子是什麼意思
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.28,0:07:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}我的事你懂個屁啊\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.95,0:07:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}想幹架嗎 你這色小鬼 啊?\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真煩死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真是會實現別人願望的神明嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您好 我是快捷便宜又放心的外派神明夜斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:07:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪音 有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.02,0:07:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.21,0:08:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的委託呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼也一起過來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有意見的話就想辦法治好我的體質
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.18,0:08:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尾巴?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.69,0:08:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假裝委託 想要暗算我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,東風若吹起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.49,0:08:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,務使庭香乘風來 枯枝滿梅花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.92,0:08:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,縱失主 亦勿忘春日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是菅原道真的和歌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.15,0:09:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學問之神{\fscx200}—{\fscx100}天神大人!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.07,0:09:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 認出來了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.94,0:09:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位活幽靈小姐真是博學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這歌很老了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教科書上有教過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.09,0:09:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傷腦筋了 著作權怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.03,0:09:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個只保持到死後50年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.97,0:09:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.16,0:09:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好有神明範兒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在太莊嚴了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦啊啦 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相比之下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 夜斗君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.57,0:09:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fsp0\bord1.5}\h             Yuki                 Setsu\N{\r}名為雪 器為雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喚作雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.18,0:09:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪音君 你剛剛成為神器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:09:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神器不必叩拜我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:09:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅雨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在自身侍奉的神明面前叩拜其他神明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乃失禮之行徑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,煩請牢記
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.19,0:10:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然有好多巫女在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是步喻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.48,0:10:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是南喻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是實喻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是望喻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天神姐妹組合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她們啊 都是我的神器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.41,0:10:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,養活她們很費力的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的神明就是不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了 找我什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs30\bord0\1a&H70\c&H000000&\org(745,592)\frx0\fry9\frz357.866\pos(964,273)}希望能考上志願的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs30\bord0\1a&H70\c&H000000&\org(398,699)\frx0\fry8\frz1.634\pos(641,146)}第一志願\N希望大家都能考上高中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs30\bord0\1a&H70\c&H000000&\frx0\fry8\org(165,687)\pos(311,531)\frz2.286}希望中考能夠考上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,705)}啊 我最近很忙嘛 因為是考試季
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.77,0:10:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望找人幫我斬個妖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正你很閒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:11:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你擅自在我家神社睡覺的事我知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你加入我的天滿集團也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你分店店長做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.57,0:11:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要自己的神社吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.05,0:11:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我這只有大鈔了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.25,0:11:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能找開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀 那些夠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貧富差距都蔓延到這邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說世道不公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這不是有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 勞你帶路了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.99,0:11:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.01,0:11:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公 真喻來此時日尚淺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶路還應請其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唔 可是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.92,0:11:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}不是假幣吧\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.85,0:11:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真喻很熟悉夜斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伴音!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是伴音 是真喻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伴音 你{\rsymbol}…{\r}竟然抱了這麼個大腿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是真喻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我之前曾做過夜斗先生的神器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.60,0:12:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當初工作方面如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.63,0:12:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有好好完成委託嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衣食住行方面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.69,0:12:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙真是居無定所無職無業的運動衫男?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.16,0:12:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是居無定所無職無業的 自稱是神明的運動衫男
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少捧一捧前任主人啊 伴音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是真喻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別用過去的名字叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,髒死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.84,0:12:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被我碰一下就牢騷滿腹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻跑來當老頭子的煙管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你掉錢眼裡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.82,0:12:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要不跟著你 跟著誰都行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:12:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你{\rsymbol}…{\r}你們原來是戀人?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.56,0:13:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原夫婦嗎 鬧得相當僵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都說不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.33,0:13:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什麼 反正很僵啊
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.78,0:13:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}髒死了是什麼意思\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別靠近我
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.08,0:13:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}有種你再說一遍\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們法庭上見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您找夜斗是委託除妖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妖是如此邪惡的存在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼一定要消滅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人心若冷天亦冷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是叫日和吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過份介入這邊的事可不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.01,0:13:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們這些人總是多愁善感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:13:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前幾天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人供上了一個有些奇怪的匾額
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\bord0\1a&H50\fn方正准圆_GBK\fsp0\frz0\c&H000000&\pos(413,364)}為了天國的朋友\N一定要考上大學\N{\fscx470}\h{\fscx100}夏希
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,調查過發現
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.93,0:14:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經死去兩人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.65,0:14:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這附近常有時化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是被循其而來的妖憑依 生了心魔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道真大人為此倍感心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡施加了結界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但人帶著心魔出入{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很難完全淨化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生命如此寶貴 真是可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 只要消滅那個憑依人的妖就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人死掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不想做些什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想死的傢伙去死就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.91,0:15:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是一如既往地渣到驚人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.04,0:15:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說 沒有剛才那樣說話的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.29,0:15:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會想到自殺的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早就被心魔所佔 連神器都做不成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是死掉的 還是活著的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都無藥可救
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.34,0:15:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 閃人咯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢著 訂金呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.19,0:15:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓她一個人走掉 這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.73,0:15:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙真是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是第一次工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:16:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我該做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喚器之時則來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喚名之時則回
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如今這就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想死的傢伙去死就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不想工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但上了大學 也沒什麼想做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.61,0:16:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,壽司卷踢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕不原諒附在人身上作惡的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伙{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.26,0:16:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伴{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有一半是伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.76,0:16:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:16:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.71,0:17:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶到彼岸去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.42,0:17:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說過尾巴斷了會死的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊老實呆著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.73,0:17:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪音 接下來的道口才是正戲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.65,0:17:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一志願測定為E
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:17:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉 這下不妙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.25,0:18:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來彼岸就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.47,0:18:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好哦 很好哦
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.97,0:18:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}很好哦 很好哦\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斬掉那隻妖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別臨陣退縮哦 雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.55,0:18:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好哦 很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 來不及
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.28,0:18:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豐葦原之中津國中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,荒亂無度的彼岸之物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾 夜斗神顯聖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以此雪器斬碎降服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將業障重重之穢跡{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盡數祓除!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:18:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord1.5\fsp0}Yuki{\fscx980}\h\N{\r}雪 行了 回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才的斬擊太過火了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.59,0:19:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你雖然說想死的傢伙去死就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但還是來救了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:19:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是 不想讓他在這些傢伙面前死得輕於鴻毛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.93,0:20:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再痛苦再難過 都要好好感受生命之重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.65,0:20:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會想到自殺的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早就被心魔所佔 連神器都做不成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家 都這麼年輕稚嫩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.29,0:20:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說並非自殺{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那神器們都是仍渴望活著的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.33,0:20:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這些人面前輕生的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜斗無法原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.29,0:21:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,色鬼雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.42,0:21:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你小子 做了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是剛才那些粉末進到眼睛裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒 這個很要緊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.03,0:21:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要揉眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.84,0:21:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和 冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況下要深呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吸吸呼 來
